dct_description_sm: This collection of flat maps, prepared from March through July of 2019 by Data You Can Use, presents a variety of housing market indicators for the City of Milwaukee. All maps compare 2012 with 2017/18 city data and utilize 2010 Census tracts. For more information, please visit Data  You Can Use.
